      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Un Airona Dehli peeneffe\n to Affini pee winna/ un wiꞥſch\neemehrze ſawu Pirksiu eekſch ta\nAffins/ un likke to us ta Altara\nRaggeem/ pehz to iſlebje wiꞥſch\nto Affini us ta Altara Grihdi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Bet tohs Taankus/ un tahs\nIhkſtis/ un tohs Taankus no tahm\nAknim pee ta Grehku-Uppura/\neededsinaja wiꞥſch us to Altari/\nittin ka tas KUNGS Mohſum\nbij pawehlejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Un to Galtu/ un to Ahdu\nfadedsinaja wiꞥſch ar Ugguni ah-\nra preekſch Lehgexa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Pehz to nokawe wiꞥſch to\nDedsamu-Uppuri / un Airona\nDehli neſfe to Affini pee winna/\nun flazzija to us to Altari ap-\nfahrt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Un tee neſfe pee winna to\nDedsamu-Uppuri ſawôs Gabba-\nlös ar to Galtu/ un wiꞥſch ee-\nDedsinaja to us to Altari.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Un wiꞥſch maſgaja tahs\nEekſchas un tahs Kahjas/ un ee-\nDedsinaja tahs wirs to Dedsamu-\nUppuri us to Altari.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "15. Pehz to peeneffe wiꞥſch to\nGauschu Uppuri / un nehme ta\nGrehku-Uppura Ahſi/kaſ preekſch\nteem Laudim bija/ un nokawe to/\nun fataiſtja to par * Grehku-Up-\npuri / itt ka to pirmo.\n* Ebr: Waliod: Wiꞥſch fataiſtija to par Greh-\nkeem: -- Kristus irr preekſch mums par Greh-\nkeem darrihts : 2. Kor: 5, 21.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "16. Un wiꞥſch peeivedde to\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Un wiꞥſch peene\ndamu-Uppuri / un kan\nfatwu Sanju pillu / u\nnaja to us to Altari/\nto Rihta Dedsamu-Upp\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Pehz to nokawe\nWehrſi/ un to Aunu pe\nſchanas-Uppuri/ kas pre\nLaudim bija/ un Aaro\npeeneffe to Affini pee wi-\nwiꞥſch flazzija to us to\nkahrt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Un tohs Taan\nWehrſcha un no ta Au-\nſtu un kas tahs Eekſcha\nun tahs Ihkſtis un\nTaankus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Untee likke tohs tahm Kruhtim/un wi-\nnaja tohs Taankus us\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "21. Bet tahs Kruh-\nlabbo Plezzu kustinaj\npar Rustinaschanas - U\nKUNGA Preekſcha/\nMohſus bij pawehlejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "22. Pehz to pazehle\nſawu Rohfu us teim\nun fwehtiſa tohs / un\npehz to/ kad wiꞥſch to\nUppuri/un to Dedsamu\nun to Pateifschanas-U\nfataiſtis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "23. Tad gahje M\nAarons eekſch tahs Sa-\nTelts/ pehz nahze tee\nfwehtiſa tcheLandis. Un\nGA Godiba parahdi\nfeem Laudim.\n"
    }
  ],
